fields: Farewell to this world! To the crappy game known as "reality"!
to the world of dating sims!
Seventeen years old, born on June 6th.
I love the girls in games. I love the girls in games.
In contrast, real girls are unreasonable, snobbish, irrational, and completely beyond hope!
But one day, I signed a contract with Elsie,  a demon from Hell, I help them fall in love
in order to chase the loose souls from the emptiness in their hearts.
If I fail, the collar around my neck will activate.
A rather harsh rule, if I say so myself.
But I have cleared many kinds of dating sims, and I am known far and wide as the "God of Conquest."
There is no girl I cannot conquer!
These puny hurdles are nothing to me!
I understand you well...  I know how you feel deep inside.
This was during my conquest of Goidou Yui,  the daughter of a rich, famous family.
Apparently, the loose soul has caused Yui and me...
to switch bodies!                                    to switch bodies!
Well, this happens all the time in games.
Score one for the real world.
If we never regain our true bodies, I shall still protect you, even if it costs me my life!
Huh? You've already captured fourteen loose souls?
Yup! All thanks to my Kami-nii-sama!
Ugh, how infuriating. He's a total creep.
Huh? But my brother's so cool... every now and then.
Ah, thank you for having me.
I guess appearance doesn't matter for a buddy...
Underclassman, ghost, ramen cook, shogi player, older woman...
After racking up real-world conquests, real girls are no problem!
However, I did have trouble understanding a real-life mad scientist:
I hope nothing like that ever happens again.
Everything went wrong, and then she disappeared without a trace.
This observatory is for Luna and me alone,  so you should keep out.
I am only interested in beauty.
And the loose soul inside her shrank her down to the size of a doll.
This world contains so much beauty!
We can search for that beauty together!
I won't let you go to the moon!
Once the conquest is complete and the loose soul exorcised, the girls forget everything that transpired.
I'm the only one who remembers what happened between us.
It's about time we got started!
You have three radio shows tonight.
Followed by some additional recording at Aokawa Studios. Okay.
And the song you just did for
Can I do some studying, please? I have a test tomorrow.
Oh, I forgot all about it...
Things are getting busier by the day.
I hope I'll have time for finals.
You put so much love into your singing today.
I can feel my power returning!
Didn't I explain this a month ago?
What do you mean by "goddess"? And what are you doing here?
One moment, I was sealing the Weiss, and next thing I knew, I was here.
What I do know is that...
This and that and something else happened, and now I'm here!
I am a descendant of Apollo, god of the arts.
My divine blessing is just perfect for you!
Diana wants to talk to you.
Why must you always be so cold?
You were just reunited with Tenri after ten long years, and you even shared a kiss.
I was simply putting on an act to get rid of Nora.
Anyway, when did that thing appear?
This ring is the symbol of the goddesses.
Your people would refer to us
Well, there's a demon standing right next to us.
And if there are demons,  there are bound to be gods.
I'm glad you're so quick to understand.
However, the moment you said you weren't a loose soul, you stopped being my problem.
I want you to marry Tenri.
Loose souls feed on negative energy, while goddesses require the power of love to grow.
To fuel my power, I require more love.
If you marry Tenri, she will be happy, and my power will return. That is why...
Why must you be so difficult?
You should pay more attention to Tenri.
She even moved in next door to you, but you spend all your time on other girls.
You can start by walking to school together every morning.
She comes to school for tests!
You sure are popular! You're like a walking spectacle!
Kids... This is your day of reckoning!
Her popularity hasn't faded one bit.
Apollo, is it okay if I talk to someone about you?
Blabbing about me to humans won't get you anywhere.
Then, do you have a plan?
To be honest, I'm not the sharpest tool in the shed.
I'm a holy maiden. Thinking isn't my forte.
If Diana was here,  she'd think of something for sure.
My younger sister.  She's super smart!
We're not getting anywhere by ourselves! We need someone we can rely on.
You just want an excuse to talk to Katsuragi Keima, don't you?
I can see the love blossoming inside you.
You only spent a week with Katsuragi, right?
that you're still pining after him.
Only because you're so set on avoiding me.
I told you to walk to school with Tenri.
Why are you walking around with an umbrella?
People will notice the ring above my head otherwise.
What happens if someone touches it?
Why are you here in our world?
A while back, you mentioned that you sealed the loose souls long ago.
Does your presence here relate to the trouble we've been having?
To be honest, I myself don't know.
Before everything began, there were three worlds
all linked by the flow of souls.
The humans, bearers of souls, lived on Earth.
After death, their souls went to Hell, where they were purified.
Heaven restored those souls to humans.
The souls flowed through the realms in a grand cycle.
However, the ancient demons of Old Hell began to manipulate humans into evildoing
in order to fatten their souls and increase their energy yield.
Then, they concocted a frightening scheme.
They planned to lay waste to Heaven, turning Earth into a graveyard of stranded souls, so as to rule all three worlds.
And I'm guessing the modern demons were the ones who opposed them.
The ones who banished the ancient demons known as Weiss
were gods from Heaven: we, the Jupiter Sisters.
The ancient demons had Heaven in their sights.
As we were goddesses of great power, we sacrificed ourselves to seal away the ancient demons and eliminate the threat.
But apparently, the seal has been broken, bringing gods and ancient demons to Earth.
Yes. When I awakened, I was already here.
Now then, you mentioned that you have sisters?
It's possible that they've also arrived on Earth.
If that is the case, I want to find them.
Could you help me look for my sisters?
I'd be relying on you to lead the effort.
...there was a loose soul attached to my body.
I assume it was put there as camouflage
to hide me among the escaping souls.
If the other goddesses are on Earth, they will likely be in a similar state.
In other words, you'll find one where you found the other.
Therefore, we can conclude that there may be goddesses
within the girls you've liberated from loose souls.
I need you to check each of them again.
Since when is that my problem?
I've already got my hands full chasing loose souls!
I can't just run off with no leads!
I do have a lead! Which would be?
The other girls who host goddesses retain their memories of you, just as Tenri does!
Once a loose soul is exorcised, the host's memories of the event are erased.
But if one of us goddesses is within them, our own memories will fill the gaps in theirs.
In other words, they will remember everything.
If one of the girls you've conquered is host to a goddess, she will remember you.
Looks like she's causing you trouble, too.
It's Keima-kun! But... who's that girl?
Good luck on your test! Kanon-chan!
That's not what I mean! Hey
It wasn't just a regular onlooker!
Excuse me, have we met before?
I'm exhausted, and it's making me see things.
I'm sure I just imagined it.
You're the only one I can turn to.
She and the dweeb know each other?
Are you saying you remember how we met?
You remember Seaside Hall and the roof?
I... I... I love you, Keima-kun!
I've... I've wanted to say it for so long!
Kanon-chan's in love with the dweeb?
Humans oughta stay out of this.
I can feel my power starting to return, thanks to you.
Can't be getting innocent bystanders involved, you know?
Having said that, I still can't fly.
So I'd better find somewhere to hide!
So you're the one who's been following me!
Damn it! Why are you after me?
As long as you goddesses are around, we cannot revive the glorious Hell of yore.
I should've realized something was wrong sooner.
So that this never happens again, I will go conquest crazy!
Become an idol! You must become an idol!
You dare to attack a goddess?
You can kill me, but my sisters...
I suppose I should finish the job.
I was so close to seeing her... How could this happen?
It's the magic of Old Hell.
The power instilled in this sword
is assassination magic used by the Weiss my sisters and I sealed so long ago.
But magic from Old Hell is forbidden!
Anyone caught using it  will wish they got thrown in jail!
Does this mean some of the Weiss have revived?
This is the insignia of Vintage.
A cult of modern demons who seek  to revive Old Hell by any means necessary.
They wouldn't think twice  about using magic like this.
There is assassination magic in today's Hell,  but this is far stronger.
An ordinary human would instantly be drained of their energy and die.
The power of the goddess is sustaining her for now, but it won't last. Eventually, she'll...
Tell us how many days she has left.
From here on, let's focus on  the information we have.
Huh? That information will determine the options I have available.
Options? How can you talk about this like a dating sim?!
Nii-sama, you have to help her!
Kanon-chan is in love with you!
Provided the conditions are met. First, I'll need information.
Conditions? Her life is on the line!
In order to do what's best, I need information.
How many days does Kanon have to live?
Once the miasma spreads throughout her body, she'll die.
The goddesses are the strongest weapons we have against the ancient demons.
They're the ones who sealed  the Weiss once before, right?
Yes, but I do not currently possess sufficient power to extract this.
What if you had another goddess to help you?
Well... If my other sisters were here,  we could do anything.
Understood. I'll find the goddesses before the week is over.
This Vintage cult is likely  targeting the others as we speak.
It's written in the ancient language of Heaven.
We have been betrayed by Hell. "Trust no one."
My sisters will be on their guard, though that means they'll be even further from our reach.
That's for the best. It's one less thing to worry about.
It seems like you have a plan in mind already.
For the time being, I shall go into hiding.
Don't contact me unless absolutely necessary.
How many sisters do you have?
One week to find four goddesses.
Do you know how many times I called? Everyone's waiting for you!
She used her raiment to change her hair.
The rest is an illusion spell. To other humans, she looks like Kanon.
But to us, she just looks like Elsie in disguise.
That takes care of Kanon's absence.
Oh, you work with my husband?
Your husband is at death's door.
That gets Mom out of the way for a while.
Now I can focus on the problem at hand.
Haqua, come to my house tomorrow morning.
Huh? You and I will search for the goddesses.
For the next week, you'll be my buddy.
So, how do we go about searching for the goddesses?
The goddesses are inside the targets I previously conquered.
Huh? How do you know that?
Diana is in Tenri, and Apollo is in Kanon.
Also, according to Diana, a girl who is host to a goddess will remember the conquest.
Kanon left us a present that should do the trick.
Kanon-chan confessed her love to him.
The more the rumors spread, the easier it will be to flush out potential goddess hosts.
It's simple. If one of my targets hosts a goddess and remembers the conquest, she'll still be in love with me.
How can you be so calm about this?
After hearing about Kanon's confession, she won't be very happy.
If any of my targets are mad at me,  they're a potential host.
Hey, how does Elsie usually act at school?
Exactly as you are now. Just flounder around.
I can't go in with you standing there.
Hello. Long time no see, Minami-chan.
A list of the girls I've conquered.
After today's investigation,  I can narrow it down to five.
My theory is that the girls most closely related to me are host to goddesses.
These names are listed in the order of most to least close to me.
Confirmed goddesses: Tenri, my childhood friend and neighbor, and Kanon, my classmate.
Two more of my classmates, Ayumi and Chihiro, I confirmed that Kusunoki in third year
had her memories wiped during my conquest of Hinoki.
And today I determined that Minami, who's a grade below me, remembers nothing either.
In other words, it's likely that no girls outside of  my own grade are host to goddesses.
The remaining girls on the right are also unlikely hosts, given their low encounter rates.
So I can disregard those to the  right of the line for this mission.
I also confirmed that Mio doesn't remember.
But aren't you just going off their relationships to you?
I may have had this all backwards.
The goddesses need love to restore their power.
We've determined that two of them reside within my prior conquests.
Perhaps I was chosen as a buddy
in order to help revive the goddesses.
My purpose is to provide the love that's required to awaken them.
If that's not the case,  then the one arranging this scenario sorely lacks in competence.
I can't keep up with all your leaps of logic!
I have but one week to complete my conquests.
I need only rely on what's most probable. Time to go home.
Starting today, you should stay with me.
No one else is there right now!
I can't be there alone with you!
She should be okay for now.
Haqua, I will cease to be a god.
I don't care what anyone else thinks, but I don't want you to get the wrong idea.
A-Are you insane?! You stupid idiot jerk!
Chihiro should be back soon. She just went to the store to get some of their new pork buns.
Why are you confessing your love to everyone?
If we simply revive the goddesses and nothing more, Vintage will come after them.
Goddesses need love to fuel their power.
At the moment, the rumors about Kanon have the girls feeling down.
But when they overcome mishaps and misunderstandings like these, I need the girls to fall in love with me once more.
I have to reach their endings again  to give the goddesses back their powers.
But there are five potential hosts.
I'll just have to conquer them all at the same time.
At the same time? You're disgusting!
No idea what you're talking about.
It's not what you think! What?!
He's following this script to the letter.
I don't want you to get the wrong idea.
Wha... What's this? How can you say that with a straight face?
Get away from me, you cockroach.
You could at least vary your lines a bit.
Her anger hasn't subsided, and I set up our next encounter.
I'll need your help with the next one.
Walk home with either Chihiro or Ayumi, and make sure they don't run into each other.
Ellie, wanna grab some cake before we go home?
Luna, the next full moon isn't for a while, so there's no point in looking at the sky.
Sorry. Are you upset about Kanon?
There's nothing between Kanon and me!
I don't know what you're talking about.
What do you think you're doing, you animal?!
I never want to see your face again!
S-Sure. It's due back in two weeks.
You're Katsuragi-kun, right? Elsie's older brother?
I see you all the time during band practice.
I'm Goidou Yui, from class A. Nice to meetcha.
I wanna talk with you some more.
I wanna know more about you.
I knew from the moment I saw you that you were the one for me.
B-But... Haven't you heard about Kanon and me?
What do you two think you're doing?!
Elsie, don't we have band practice today?
Chihiro and Ayumi didn't show up, either.
The Mai High Festival is coming up,  so we need all the practice we can get!
Well, I'll see you around, Katsuragi-kun.
Please be quiet in the librarian!
She doesn't remember the conquest itself,  but her love is still in effect?
Since she confessed to me,  she's a potential host.
Then the five possible hosts are
Kujou Tsukiyo, Goidou Yui, Takahara Ayumi, Kosaka Chihiro, and Shiomiya Shiori.
Four of them are hosting goddesses.
Katsuragi? Why did you pick up?
Elsie can't come to the phone right now, so I said I'd pass on a message for her.
She said she wants to walk home with you tomorrow, and to wait in the classroom after school.
No idea. That's just what she said.
I don't get that at all, but fine. Bye.
Katsuragi, what was that all about?
Preparation for tomorrow's  "leaving school simultaneously" event.
Huh? I'm done looking for hosts.
It's time for the next stage.
You're good, but even you can't conquer five girls at once.
If you can't court multiple girls simultaneously, you can't play dating sims.
I'd like to say it's a cakewalk, but in the real world, it takes time to move around.
Can't I just load from a save point?
You're walking home from school with them?
I already have my list of potential goddess hosts.
All that remains is to get close to them.
Is walking home with them really that important?
1) Walk home together! 2) Exchange contact information.
3) Go on a date. 4) The girl invites you to walk home together.
Walking home together is the very first step!
If you can't get that part down, you'll remain a novice in the art of love forever.
I'll follow this schedule. One hour for each of the five!
I'll raise my affection level  with each girl by five points!
Hey, Ellie! You're all fired up!
Why isn't she here yet? I'm already an hour behind schedule!
I hate the rain. Luna, did you get wet?
I waited for you so that we could walk home together.
Stay away from me, you sick freak!
I need to make up for lost time!
I don't know where all these rumors about Kanon-chan and me came from.
I know tomorrow's Sunday, but will you be in the astronomy clubroom?
If the night sky is clear.
Yes! I have permission to enter!
You've really got your part down.
You must have practiced hard. Oh, you think so?
Should we call it a day? Sounds good!
You were supposed to buy me more time!
Well then, ladies, I'll take my leave.
You're a lady too, you know.
Um, why don't we talk for a bit?
Oh yeah, Ellie, didn't you  need me for something?
I got a call from Katsuragi last night.
So, what did you wanna talk about?
I'm off to a bad start...
I was waiting for you  so we could walk home together.
Ayumi, how did you do on the last test?
I'd guess that you Hey, Katsuragi...
If you walk home with us,  won't Kanon-chan get mad at you?
Yeah, I never would've expected Katsuragi and Kanon-chan as a couple.
Oh! I wanna hear about it too!
Oh, I'm just dying to have some of the taiyaki here! Huh?
Hey! What are you doing?! What's this about? Let's go inside!
How about that music store we always go to?
Katsuragi, you wanted sweet bean filling, right?
It's still hot, so I'll wrap  another napkin around it for you.
No point being nice to me now.
If a loose soul gets inside you,  I'm not gonna help.
Chihiro said she wanted to visit the music store.
They all just have to do things their own way...
You realize how important  these conquests are, don't you?
Were you just talking to someone?
No, not really... Uh, did you need something?
I... I don't have time to waste on you!
So don't talk to me anymore!
I will continue to follow you around!
Let me go Sorry, but nothing you say will stop me.
Ellie sure is taking her time... Does she have a stomachache or something?
Elsie asked me to pick up some bass strings.
But I can't figure out which ones to get.
Where's Ellie? Something came up, so she had to go.
What's the point of having so many different guitars, anyway?
Well, I'm still a beginner. I've only been playing guitar for six months.
What's with the price? Think of how many games you could buy with that.
Oh, Katsuragi... Stand over here with me. It's too embarrassing on my own.
Well? Did the expensive one sound better?
I couldn't even tell. I was way too nervous.
What was that song you were singing?
The plan is for us to perform an original song at the Mai High Festival, but I've only written the first part.
You can't judge a song by the intro
Why am I talking to you about this?!
Oh, Ellie... Pay for your brother's taiyaki, okay?
That just makes my job easier.
My name is Simone. "Simone S. Libro!"
I've become a galactic reporter! It's like a dream come true!
It is our responsibility to denounce the crimes committed in this war.
So why is there an article on space dumplings?
I have a bad habit of saying everything that comes to mind.
I wish I could learn to keep my mouth shut.
Books are wonderful. "They are the enduring legacy of the human race."
Books are just a relic of the past.
Please don't write in the books.
We've been talking a lot lately.
Simone, you're like a main character.
I'm too scared to go into space.
Very well. "I'll give you the courage you need."
I added something to the end.
Thanks to my space body armor, I escaped without a scratch!
Who said you could come back to life?! "Don't add stupid twists like that!"
I just wanted to see you again.
Why do you keep coming back to life? "I don't ever want to see you again!"
And Kashiragi isn't supposed to talk this much!
I want to spend more time with you.
Can I help you with your story on nebula ramen?
Okay. The story can be continued.
But my goal is to trigger a "leaving school" event.
Watch from above, and tell me when Shiori leaves.
Why are you here? I saw you take a car home!
I wanted to walk home with you.
I spotted you from the car.
It's pretty dangerous out on the streets these days, so I couldn't let a helpless boy walk home all on his own.
Hey, wait a minute! That's something that boys say to girls!
You're up later! Don't trigger events on your own!
I don't need you to walk me home.
I'm a man, so allow me to escort you.
That made my heart skip a beat.
Every now and then, you have  the most wonderful look on your face...
But earlier, I saw you look at  Ayumi and Chihiro the same way.
I didn't think you were such a playboy.
It's an item you'll definitely need in the future.
The hell am I supposed to do with this?!
It'd be strange to see a couple where both people wore male uniforms, right?
Why don't you dress like a girl?!
You'll get used to it soon enough.
I don't want to get used to it! And we're not a couple!
I realize that you may be a bad person, but I will teach you true love!
It's not true love if we're both cross-dressing!
Don't worry. Love will conquer all.
Today, we caught Kanon after a recording session.
Guess I'll go see all of them.
Why is Nora here? Does she know about Kanon?
But she's a colleague of mine! She wouldn't go that far...
Hey, don't ignore me! Is Elsie around?
I'm just passing on a message.
Listen to me. Don't let her find Kanon.
You're a good deal more useful than my stupid buddy.
I'm glad that you like me!
Why are you sucking up to her?
I changed my mind. We need to pump her for information.
Hey, Nora? Why do you need to talk to Elsie?
We have new orders from the bureau.
Apparently, we're looking for residents of Heaven  who've gone into hiding on Earth.
No one told me anything about that!
The official announcement will be tomorrow.
They're talking about the goddesses, right? That means...
I need you to negotiate with Nora  so we can squeeze information out of her.
This school is full of potential goddesses.
If this were a game, there'd be some secret  plot element explaining why they're all here.
You'd better not be the last goddess!
Well, I'll be heading off. Huh?
Tell Elsie to come see me when she gets back.
What is this? Is it... Kanon?!
But it's really hard to not criticize that story...
Huh? Why did it suddenly get dark?
Whatever. Next up is Ayumi or Chihiro...
The miasma is definitely getting stronger!
Did you really think I wouldn't notice miasma seeping into the hallway?
What's going on? I want an explanation.
Vintage put a curse on her.
The fate of New Hell rests on whether she lives or dies.
Is this some kind of prank?! What did I ever do to you?!
I am Vulcanus, a goddess who values justice and intricacy.
This is a warning. Never go near Tsukiyo again.
Tsukiyo is a beautiful girl. More beautiful than anything I have ever seen.
I will not allow an unfaithful, dirty, and dangerous man like you to associate with her.
What have I done You were getting quite friendly with the library girl.
I saw you with my own eyes.
I was aware that you had received something from that girl.
You'd better clean up the mess you made!
My vision and hearing are poor. I cannot walk.
I send my soul into other things, turning them into my eyes and limbs.
Objects are all I need to protect Tsukiyo.
Let me talk to Tsukiyo! Tsukiyo!
I feel the same way Luna does.
You never came to see me again.
On top of that, you've been spending a lot of time  with that singer and the library girl.
You mean nothing to me! I hate you!
You creepy doll! Let me through!
I want to talk to Tsukiyo!
Tsukiyo says that she doesn't want to see you.
If you wish to speak to her,  you'll have to get past me.
Why are you doing this to me?!
You cheated on her with that singer, Kanon, and then you had the audacity to  make a move on the library girl too!
I have no idea what you're talking about. You must be confused.
Liars like you get buried by benches,  crushed into paste, and plunged into the depths of Hell!
How could she trust you, you demon? Leave at once!
I refuse! I won't leave until I've talked with Tsukiyo!
So why did this cruel man  have to come back into my life?
Inevitable?! How can you say such an irresponsible thing
We were brought together by fate.
How can you say it was fate?
Why did you come back? Why?
I was so close to forgetting about you...
A kiss will solve all of our problems!
What? In the end, it comes down to the kiss!
Being with you will corrupt Tsukiyo.
I will not let you see Tsukiyo again.
You should hurt me more than that.
You're absolutely right. I've hurt Tsukiyo.
And I can't guarantee that I won't make her unhappy.
How dare you speak so indifferently?!
Leave before I drop these on you.
I'm willing to accept any punishment.
I need you to love me for just a little longer!
Otherwise, I won't be able to protect you!
Can I trust you? Can I really trust you, Keima?
This world is filled with beautiful things.
Let's search for them! You and I, together!
Luna, are you trying to kill Keima?
I lost control because you interfered.
This man just doesn't know when to give up.
Luna, we should talk to Keima about your sisters.
My existence must remain a secret.
How can you say that after everything you did?
Do you really trust this man?
So why did they target this girl?
If you wait too long, they'll revive Old Hell.
The Loose Souls Team won't allow that to happen.
You think the Loose Souls Team are the good guys here?
Haven't you heard the rumors about Vintage worming their way into the Loose Souls Team?
They're within the Loose Souls Team?!
The order to search for the goddesses
is essentially an order to capture the goddesses.
I wonder who issued the order.
So, Apollo is inside this girl...
Are we all living inside human girls right now?
I am Diana. It's been so long, Nee-sama.
Our appearances may have changed, but I am overjoyed to see you again.
It appears that the time has come for us to be reunited.
Let us join our powers together.
By the way, Nee-sama... What are those things on your back?
On my back? These are my wings. What about them?
However, I still find it hard to believe that we are being targeted.
Apollo was even brought to death's door.
Right, I need the two of you to remove Apollo's curse.
I need you to come upstairs.
You could have just turned back into Tsukiyo.
I don't see a problem. You've carried Tsukiyo around before.
This means that Nee-sama has recovered more power.
Did you engage in a special act of love with her?
One that you didn't do with Tenri?
Now, enough of that hushed chatter.
Diana may be my sister, but you should not speak so freely to other women.
After all, you are an important source of power for Tsukiyo and myself.
How did you recover your power?
We can talk about this later. We have more important matters to deal with right now!
It pains me to see her like this.
I wasn't able to remove the curse by myself.
